Structs/IndexedSymbolName.html#/s:10Pars.name: name
Structs/IndexedSymbolName.html#/s:10Pars.abstract: The name of the terminal or nonterminal that this indexed symbol designates.

Structs/IndexedSymbolName.html#/s:10Pars.name: hasIndex
Structs/IndexedSymbolName.html#/s:10Pars.abstract: Whether this symbol has an index or not. An index of 0 counts as having no index.

Structs/RuleName.html.name: RuleName
Structs/RuleName.html.abstract: The name of a rule. Must be anonymous or otherwise unique among the other names of rules belonging to the same symbol.

Structs/SymbolName.html.name: SymbolName
Structs/SymbolName.html.abstract: The type of the name of a Symbol.

Structs/IndexedSymbolName.html.name: IndexedSymbolName
Structs/IndexedSymbolName.html.abstract: An IndexedSymbol designates either a terminal or a nonterminal.

Classes/TerminalPriorityId.html#/s:10Par.name: init()
